OL,3,CLawyer guilty of sexual assault for
OL,4,Ctouching bums on night out
OL,6,FA Guernsey lawyer has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of two counts of sexual assault
OL,8,Fafter touching the bottoms of two
OL,9,Fwomen in a bar.
OL,11,FThe Royal Court heard how Steven
OL,12,FBalmer, aged 39 and a senior associate
OL,13,Ffor Carey Olsen, approached the two
OL,14,Fwomen who were with a group of people
OL,15,Fhe knew at the Hook bar in St Peter
OL,16,FPort on the evening of Saturday 29
OL,17,FMarch last year.
