OL,4,Ctouching bums on night out
OL,6,FOver the course of the evening, the
OL,7,Fcourt heard how Balmer made repeated
OL,8,Fsexualised comments towards one of the
OL,9,Fwomen.
OL,11,FThese included references to her
OL,12,Fbreasts, her physique and the clothes
OL,13,Fshe was wearing, including him asking
OL,14,Fher, "How fit do you need to be to
OL,15,Fcheat on your husband?".
OL,17,FShe shared her concerns with her
OL,18,Fspouse through text messages, which
OL,19,Fwere read out to the court.
