OL,6,FThey included, "He's just spent the
OL,7,Flast 10 minutes telling me how fit I
OL,8,Fam".
OL,10,FThen, some time later, "He gives me
OL,11,Fserial killer vibes, he's still going".
OL,13,FCCTV footage, which was played to the
OL,14,Fcourt, shows the two women standing at
OL,15,Fthe bar before Balmer touched one of
OL,16,Fthem on the buttocks and the other on
OL,17,Fthe lower backside.
