OL,6,FThe court heard how, in a police
OL,7,Finterview after the incident, Balmer
OL,8,Fsaid, "From my perspective, I
OL,9,Fappreciate it wasn't to cop and feel.
OL,10,FIt was just to get their attention.
OL,11,FFrom my perspective, it wasn't
OL,12,Fanything sexual."
OL,14,FBodycam footage of the women reporting
OL,15,Fthe crime showed one of them in tears.
OL,16,FShe gave the police officer a business
OL,17,Fcard that Balmer had given her.
OL,19,FShe said, "He's a lawyer, he probably
OL,20,Fknows judges. A judge isn't going to
OL,21,Flisten to me".
