OL,6,FShe added, "How many times did I tell
OL,7,Fhim I was married? About 50."
OL,9,FBalmer had pleaded not guilty to the
OL,10,Fassaults and when giving evidence,
OL,11,Fsaid he did not recall making any
OL,12,Fsexualised comments and that the mood
OL,13,Fof the conversation with the women was
OL,14,Fbenign, pleasant and jovial.
OL,16,FHe added that a lot of the time, he
OL,17,Fwas reassuring the women rather than
OL,18,Ftrying to make any sexual advances
OL,19,Ftowards them and that they laughed at
OL,20,Fsome of his comments.
