OL,6,FWhen asked about touching the two
OL,7,Fwomen on the buttocks, he said he did
OL,8,Fnot recall the incident. This was
OL,9,Fdespite the court being shown CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage that showed him touching them
OL,11,Fboth on the backside.
OL,13,FHe said he remembered leaving the bar
OL,14,Fand, from the evidence he was shown,
OL,15,Fcontact with the women was fleeting.
OL,17,FBalmer will be back in Guernsey's
OL,18,FRoyal Court for sentencing in April.
